full_summary:
# Tender Notice for Biological Assessment and Management Services
 [Tender No. WS4077572617](http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/16730662?extsite=MTY3MzA2NjJfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg== "Tender Details")

## Tender Overview
The Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC) is soliciting a Request for Proposal (RFP) for Biological Assessment and Management Services in various locations in British Columbia and Yukon. Biological assessments and management services encompass terrestrial, marine, and freshwater environments.

## Contract Details
* **Contract Value**: Up to $1,500,000.00 (excluding applicable taxes)
* **Contract Term**: 3 years, with an option to extend for an additional 1-year period
* **Number of Contracts to be Awarded**: Up to 3

## Tender Criteria and Evaluation
The tender evaluation criteria will be based on a total combined rating of technical merit and price. The highest combined rating will be selected as the winner.

## Rules and Trade Agreements
This tender is subject to the Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA), Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA), North American Free Trade Agreement (NAFTA), Free Trade Agreement between Canada and Ukraine (CUFTA), and other applicable trade agreements.

## Contact Information
Please contact Adrianne Dunsmore, Senior Contracting Authority, for more information:
* **Email**: [adrianne.dunsmore@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca](mailto:adrianne.dunsmore@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca)
* **Phone**: [Not Provided]
* **Fax**: [Not Provided]

## Tender Closing Date
* **Tender Closing Date**: 2023-08-02T14:00:00
* **Late Submissions WILL NOT BE ACCEPTED**
